  "texts": [
    "Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) has emerged as a promising solution by enabling language models to reference external knowledge sources dynamically during inference [2].",
    "LangChain, a modular orchestration framework, further enhances RAG pipelines by enabling chain-of-thought reasoning and custom prompt workflows [3].",
    "When combined with high-performance vector databases like Facebook AI Similarity Search (FAISS) [4] or Chroma DB [5], enterprises can embed and index internal documents to build robust, scalable knowledge retrieval systems.",
    "This integration empowers conversational agents to generate more accurate, relevant, and context-rich responses.",
    "This paper introduces a domain-aware chatbot framework that combines GPT-3.5, LangChain, and local vector storage to create a secure, real-time question-answering assistant."
